Package: fiber
Type: Package
Title: S7 Data Structures for Diffusion MRI Tractography
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Aymeric",
        family = "Stamm",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "aymeric.stamm@cnrs.fr",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8725-3654")
    ))
Description: Provides two S7 classes — 'streamline' and 'bundle' — for
    representing diffusion MRI tractography data in R, together with a concise
    set of methods for computing shape descriptors (arc-length, curvature,
    torsion, sinuosity), the Hausdorff distance between streamlines,
    arc-length reparametrization of streamlines and bundles onto uniform grids,
    and combination of streamlines or bundles into a single bundle.
